  "text": "In patients with PKU, every 4 week delay in starting treatment results in a decline of approximately four intelligence quotient (IQ) points, [CITATION_1] which underscores the knowledge that neurological damage starts early after birth. Therefore, the organisation of newborn screening and referral to PKU centres is strongly advocated so that treatment is started no later than 10 days of age.",
